	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=120472><span id= >Kalendrox</span></a><br><span id=notbold>139 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.23]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>just my 2 cents on this.<br><br>As a Master Tailor on Innoruuk (175) I can tell you that while Acrylia Reinforced isnt too difficult to make, (very sucessfull even with a 244 trivial),&nbsp;&nbsp;this is not an item that you will see for sale very often, for several reasons.  First off, all Acrylia Reinforced trivials at the same level, which means its just as hard to make a reinforced tunic as it is to make a reinforced mask.  Secondly, the profit margin for this item is very small.  You may spend 100p for the components, but you probably wont be able to sell this for more than 300p.  In comparison, you can spend 200p on the components for the Reinforced tunic, but sell that for 3500p.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Jun  2 17:27:56 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br>Kalendrox Grimblade<br>Dread Lord of the Heretics<br>Innoruuk<br><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=76892" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=76892</a></td></td></tr>
